<p>UIC will continue normal operations today.</p>
<p>While we realize that weather differs across the Chicagoland area, conditions in the city and on campus are wet but accessible.</p>
<p>All employees are urged to use their discretion in deciding whether they can safely commute to and from campus. If personal safety or health is an issue in that decision, responsible judgment should be used. Employees who cannot report to work must use personal time (vacation, floating holiday, accrued comp time) or take an excused, unpaid absence.</p>
<p>As a reminder, please call the 24/7 phone number, 5-SNOW (312-355-7669) to report any snow- or ice-related problems on campus.</p>
